data.description: Hard to find 4 bedroom 2 full bath Ranch (Primary bedroom has an ensuite bath) and as a bonus is in the Grosse Pointe School district! The living room has new Wallside windows with a transferable life time guarantee and opens into the dining room. There are hardwood floors throughout and a new tear off roof in 2022. Carpeted recreation room 44x25 offers additional space for fun or storage! There is a 2 1/2 car garage with door opener and fenced back yard.  The front double doors and porch add to this homes curb appeal!!!!
